</p><p class="- topic/p "> Be aware that the Standard Warranty program may vary depending on your geographic location, please contact your Authorised Service Organization for more information. 
</p></section><section id="GUID-52A9E351-C195-4B79-9FEF-0BD3E7F13421" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Standard Warranty on hardware</title><p class="- topic/p "> Canon warrants the hardware of its Colorado Series to be free from manufacturer’s defects in material and workmanship, during the first two years since installation or the first 20.000 sqm printed (according to counter 218508) whichever occurs first. Terms and conditions apply, according to the official statement. 
</p></section><section id="GUID-CDDF2251-F7D2-4DA3-8022-5582D4A2A5DD" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Standard Warranty on printheads</title><p class="- topic/p ">Canon warrants the printheads of its Colorado series to be free from manufacturer’s defects in material and workmanship, during the first two years from the date of installation in the Canon Colorado Series printer or the first 20.000 sqm printed by the printhead (according to counter 48034), whichever occurs first. Terms and conditions apply, according to the official statement. 
